 products online go to the home tab and select manager tools in the submenu choose settings and click on general setup  options under general settings expand the online store settings section check the box to enable the first option sell your own products online click update on the right side of the screen youll also want to set up shipping click here to learn more   to enable individual products that will be sold online home tab and select products in the submenu click on the search button and review all products or enter search criteria to narrow the results check the box in the sold online column for any product that you want to sell online if you want to sell all products in your search results online then click the check all link at the top of the column you can also check the sold online boxes when you add products to the system   how your clients will purchase products from your online store after logging in to your site clients will need to click on the online store tab and then click on products in the toolbar near the top of the screen a variety of products will display on the screen they can narrow down the search for products by selecting a specific category on the left side of the screen eg clothing equipment when they find an item they want to buy theyll click on it if applicable a new screen will appear where they can choose an item size or color note clients to can purchase an unlimited quantity of products next clients will click on the add to cart button to add this item to the shopping cart when finished shopping the clients will click on their shopping cart theyll review their orders and shipping addresses and then choose a shipping method once satisfied clients will click on the check out button after clicking on check out they will decide how they want to pay clients can choose to enter their credit card information charge the items to a credit card already on file with your business enter a prepaid gift card number in the the field at the top of the screen or apply existing account credit by clicking yes when the system asks if they would like to use it the clients email address will display at the bottom and a purchase receipt will be emailed to him or her once complete press the place order button please note that clients are unable to use ach as a method of payment when purchasing items in consumer mode from your online store back to top   pricing options and memberships to sell individual pricing options you must check the sell online checkbox in pricing options  memberships go to the home tab and select manager tools in the submenu click on pricing options under pricing scroll through the list or enter the name of the pricing option that youre looking for and click search check the box in the sold online column to enable the pricing option for online sale note a pricing option will not appear in the online store if the only use in contracts  packages checkbox is ticked when you set up the pricing option selling a pricing option online is separate from allowing your client to make an appointment or reservation online if you disable allowing clients to schedule online then you may also want to consider whether or not to allow clients to buy pricing options for those services online   how your clients will purchase services from your online store after logging into your site your client will need to click on the online store tab and then click on services the client will need to select a service category from the dropdown list and then choose a specific pricing option clients will see the actual purchase price of each item in the menu they will click add to cart when they find the one they want to buy note if you require payment when clients sign up for services then the system will automatically direct clients to the services section of your online store whenever they book an appointment or register for a class or enrollment they can then click on continue shopping near the bottom of the screen to keep adding items to the cart and they can always click on shopping cart in the toolbar at the top of the screen to double check what theyre purchasing once clients have selected all of the pricing options that they want to buy they will click on check out at the bottom of the shopping cart screen back to top   contracts  packages to sell individual contracts and packages in your online store you must check the sell online checkbox next to each item in the contracts  packages screen go to the home tab and select manager tools in the submenu click on contracts  packages under pricing from the select item menu choose a contract that you want to sell online check the box in the sell online column to the right decide whether or not you want to allow clients to cancel this contract online if so check the allow terminating in consumer mode checkbox fill in the online description this is what your clients will read in your online store when they decide which contract to buy fill in the contract text box with your terms and conditions this is what your clients will read and agree to when they purchase the contract decide whether or not you want clients to agree to read and agree to your contract when they buy it online if so check the electronic confirmation of contract box click save   how your clients will purchase contracts and packages from your online store after logging in to your site your client will need to click on the online store tab then click on contractspackages the client will choose the contract or package that he or she would like to buy from the dropdown menu if a client that wants to buy a contract that youve set up for electronic confirmation the client will need to read and agree to the contract agreement to continue next the client will click on make purchase to go to the shopping cart screen from the shopping cart the client can click on the class workshop or appointment tab to sign up for services click on retail store or online store to purchase products click on gift cardscredit check out pay for their purchase with a credit card gift card or account credit back to top   gift cards and account payments to sell gift cards and account payments online you must check the sell online box for individual gift cards and account payments prepaid gift cards go to the home tab and choose manager tools in the submenu click on gift cards under pricing  click on the name of a gift card that you want to sell online check the sell online box in the edit a gift card lightbox click save  assignable gift cards home tab and choose manager tools in the submenu click on gift cards under pricing then choose tools and select assignable gift cards choose the assignable gift card that you want to sell online check the sell online box click save how your clients will purchase gift cards from your online store if your client is purchasing a gift card in your online store then he or she will see the gift certificate designs that you selected within the choose a gift certificate layout dropdown menu to learn more about the online store gift certificate layout templates click here th client will then enter the following fields to from message optional recipients full name if the client wishes to email the gift card to the recipient then he or she can fill out the recipient email and email confirmation fields clicking on the make purchase button will take the client to the shopping cart from the shopping cart the client can click on the class enrollment or appointment tab to sign up for a service click on online store to purchase products click on gift cardscredit to purchase gift cards or account credit click check out  to pay for their purchase with credit card gift card or account credit after he or she has placed the order in the checkout screen the client will also be given the option to print the gift certificate   account payments home tab and select manager tools in the submenu click on account payments under pricing  choose the account payment that you want to sell online check the sell online box click save how do account payments work for clients on your online store an account payment gives the client a positive credit balance on his or her account with your business which can be used to purchase products and services account payments are also used as payment plan options for workshops back to top   customize option for your online store there are a slew of options in your mindbody site that affect your online store including hot words and page phrases general setup  options go to the general setup  options page in your software for more information on these features online store account purchases  allow all clients in consumer mode allow clients with autopays to edit billing info service notes in online store sell your own products online ecommerce order fulfillment location shipfrom city shipfrom stateprov shipfrom postalcode shipping methods allow in store pickup free shipping threshold allow shoppers to select faster shipping shipping weights measured in show  in stock to public hide out of stock products allow out of stock orders show logo on online gift certificate gift certificate contact information leave blank for default sizing chart url color swatch url media handshake url auto complete closed date client rewards program settings class  enrollment options go to the class  enrollment option screen in your software for more information on this feature  allow clients to purchase enrollment pricing option without enrolling by default this option is enabled and your site will allow clients to purchase an enrollment pricing option regardless of whether or not theyve made a reservation disabling  this option to restrict clients from purchasing an enrollment pricing option in the online store without making a reservation words and phrases click here to learn about hot words and page phrases that affect your online store   back to top additional resources consumer mode overview shipping ma