mber     am your relationship with your clients is fundamental to your salon’s well being mindbody’s webbased software gives you the tools to strengthen that relationship by giving your clients more flexibility and control over when and how they schedule appointments with you all for about the price of a haircut online booking once you have it you’ll never go back salon owners love online booking because it cuts down on no shows increases revenue and eliminates phone tag clients love it because it makes the salon seem more professional and it accommodates their busy lifestyle and don’t worry you decide what appointments can be booked online you can even use overlapping and double booking features to maximize your efficiency time savers send appointment confirmations automatically via email or text use the appointment finder feature to quickly see availability post tasks for staff and track stylist productivity revenue generators combine integrated credit card processing with an online store to sell products gift certificates or take advantage of rewards points for loyal customers client tracking features segment and market to clients by type eg by past services purchased color formula firsttime client age track visit and payment history and target big spenders sales  marketing reports easily generate reports that show your client retention sales by category inventory including shelf life payroll and staff performance with mindbody’s suite of mobile applications you can access your schedule from anywhere and ditch that appointment book once and for all and since mindbody backs up your client and financial records each day you’ll never have to worry about losing your data again mindbody offers a special rate for single providers of just  a month this deal is for those of you who run a “one man” or “one woman” show or only need one log most popular  why you should enter a competition and tips on howto win   myths about hair thinning and hair loss debunked  lindsey olso